Hi I found out about you from my biz partner. We got the Clickbank email to Diamond CB members. Can I get the $2000 account credit for my account?

Hi there! Yes, as a Diamond ClickBank affiliate, you are eligible to receive $2,000 in ad credits. To get started, you'll need to schedule an onboarding call with our Account Managers and complete the business verification process. You can schedule your call through this link: [NewsBreak Advertising Consultation](https://calendly.com/d/z4w-3t3-rkw/newsbreak-advertising-consultation). Once that's done, you'll be able to receive your ad credits.
how to setup click to call conversion tracking?
Could you please specify which tracking platform or service you are using for the click to call conversion tracking? This will help me provide more accurate instructions.
I have gohighlevel and I want to use the newsbreak conversion tracking to track clicks on our call buttons on the landing page

For setting up click-to-call conversion tracking with NewsBreak on your GoHighLevel landing page, you can follow the general postback integration guide. Here are the steps to integrate a general NewsBreak Postback event for tracking clicks on call buttons:
1. **Add the Callback Parameter to Your Ad's Landing Page URL**: Insert `__CALLBACK_PARAM__` into the landing page URL of your ad.
2. **Create/Test Event**: In NewsBreak Ad Manager, go to `Tools > Event Management > Web Events`, click the `Create/test event` button, then choose `Postback` as your event tracking type.
3. **Select Tracking Service**: If you're not using a 3rd party tracking service that we already support, please choose `Others` in the tracking service field.
4. **Choose Event Type**: Select the event type you want to track (e.g., click-to-call) and if you want to track event value as well.
5. **Follow Instructions**: An instruction will show based on your inputs on the platform.
For more detailed instructions, you can refer to this article: [How to integrate a general NewsBreak Postback](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/25226963388813-How-to-integrate-a-general-NewsBreak-Postback).
Let me know if you need any further assistance!
